    The main objetive is to sense  threats to individuals that may presence some type of abuse. 
    
    The application will be connected through a nework of individuals that will be notified through a group if the same "pattern" is reconigzed in different places, if the pattern is identified, it will alert the group

    After receiving the alert, people that participate of the group will rate the alert, if an higher rating is voted, the alert will be repassed to local authorities periodically

    An optional feature, is a channel where the local authorities will have an direct encrypted communication with the individuals that participate of the group
